## Description {#details}

An instantiation group contains a <code><a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/coverage/functionrecord">FunctionRecord</a></code> list, such that each record corresponds to a distinct instantiation of the same function.

Note that it&#39;s possible for a function to have more than one instantiation (consider C++ template specializations or static inline functions).
